ingredients.ingredient: 1 (5 ounce) package non-instant chocolate pudding mix

cookingTips: This is a no-mix dessert - simply layer pudding mixture, dry cake mix, and chocolate chips in the pan
Don't stir ingredients together; the layers will create a fudgy, cake-like texture as it bakes
Bake at 350°F for 40-45 minutes until a toothpick comes out with moist crumbs
enrichment.coachingPrompt: This is an unconventional dump cake that relies on layering. How will the pudding, dry cake mix, and chips transform during baking?
